WEBVTT

00:00:11.040 --> 00:02:47.839
We're live. Thank you. Center with me for a moment. Let's listen again; it's my favorite.

00:02:47.840 --> 00:04:11.919
Just center with me for a moment. It's beautiful. How many? Well, I'll get started.

00:04:11.920 --> 00:04:16.519
Good morning, family. Thank you for joining us again today.

00:04:16.519 --> 00:04:23.599
We'll go over some of the things the Lord showed us yesterday in prayer and then we'll just jump in the river.

00:04:23.600 --> 00:04:29.759
I know a lot of you have a lot of things you're going to be doing today because we're getting ready to celebrate the Fourth of July in America.

00:04:29.760 --> 00:04:37.839
And so we say, 'Happy birthday, America.'I believe it's an exciting time.

00:04:37.840 --> 00:04:48.118
I love this time of year; I love it. My birthday's today, so I get excited about that. Thank you, I appreciate that.

00:04:48.119 --> 00:04:58.699
I woke up early this morning and was talking to the Lord about my life and things that the Lord has done this year, just being grateful for everything that I have and that the Lord has blessed me with good health.

00:04:58.700 --> 00:05:10.512
I'm so thankful not just for living, but for living well—that your health is good.

00:05:10.513 --> 00:05:18.799
I know everybody has something they're overcoming and you're believing God for stuff, but for the most part, Lord, You've kept me sound and whole.

00:05:18.800 --> 00:05:43.918
Thank you. He talked about being satisfied and started talking to me about elders and some of the ones who were going home.

00:05:43.919 --> 00:05:57.580
He started telling me, 'This one will live to 78.'I said, 'Well, that's not too much longer.

00:05:57.581 --> 00:06:07.119
Why are they going to go home at that time?'He said, 'Because they're satisfied.'I said, 'Satisfied?

00:06:07.120 --> 00:06:13.719
What does that have to do with anything?'He said, 'With long life, I will satisfy you.

00:06:13.720 --> 00:06:20.318
And when you're satisfied, Brandon, you can come home.'Are you satisfied?

00:06:20.319 --> 00:06:35.599
He said you can petition Me for more years, but when you are satisfied and walking with Me in ministry, doing what you're supposed to be doing, He said, 'The number of your days I will fulfill.

00:06:35.600 --> 00:06:41.009
I will let you live until you're satisfied. When you are satisfied, I'll bring you home.

00:06:41.010 --> 00:07:05.638
I'll give you 120.'He was talking to me about being satisfied with life. I said I'm not satisfied at that age; I want to occupy.

00:07:05.639 --> 00:07:18.239
I'm not in a hurry to go to the other side if You're not coming in the Rapture, because I know there's so many people that are dying and going to hell.

00:07:18.240 --> 00:07:26.298
I'm not criticizing; that's just where I'm at. Maybe I'll be different when I get that old.

00:07:26.299 --> 00:07:35.198
Right now, because I'm only 46 today, I'm not even near. I feel like I just started my race.

00:07:35.199 --> 00:07:43.119
So I say, 'My goodness, give me double,'because I see so many people going to hell.

00:07:43.120 --> 00:07:54.079
Yesterday we had 34 people give their heart to Jesus Christ on our channel.

00:07:54.080 --> 00:08:04.048
There's a tenderness to it because it's just the beginning of what the Lord is doing.

00:08:04.049 --> 00:08:09.732
I know there'll be a lot more people born again over the next couple days watching that video, especially on my other channels.

00:08:09.733 --> 00:08:18.090
I have seven other channels in South Korea. It's so wonderful to see people that are Buddhists give their heart to Jesus Christ.

00:08:18.091 --> 00:08:26.559
Then when you have the Portuguese channel and the Brazilian, the Lord said to pray over the young man that's running it.

00:08:26.560 --> 00:08:55.812
I saw a new David rising up in Brazil and He said, 'Pray for the people of Brazil; there are so many of them.'As I talked to Pastor Maldonado, he was talking about souls and his goal of setting it up for a million people to go to Cuba and have a revival.

00:08:55.813 --> 00:09:08.879
He's already getting it ready; they're already preparing financially for what God is about to do in the Latino community. It inspires me.

00:09:08.880 --> 00:09:21.617
It stretches me because he gave me the counts of all the people that have been born again in his ministry—14 million people in over 30 years.

00:09:21.618 --> 00:09:30.261
I thought, 'Wow.'He gave me the list, giving all the glory to the Lord.

00:09:30.262 --> 00:09:47.119
Just thinking about making a lasting impact, changing a generation for Jesus, and wanting to leave your mark on this world. I believe He's coming, ladies and gentlemen.

00:09:47.120 --> 00:10:00.639
Don't get me wrong, but I know there have been generations—Sister Woodworth-Etter believed He was coming back in her timeframe in the 1800s and had signs 'Jesus is coming soon'on her banners.

00:10:00.640 --> 00:10:11.359
Kathryn Kuhlman felt that she was coming in her time. I believe Brother Hagin felt that he was coming in his time—Kenneth Hagin.

00:10:11.360 --> 00:10:21.039
So you have a generation of people that have always had that urgency inside of themselves because there's no time with the Lord.

00:10:21.040 --> 00:10:35.679
He has long patience for the harvest because He doesn't want any man to perish but all to come to repentance. So what is He looking for? What is on the Father's heart?

00:10:35.680 --> 00:10:49.039
That was my big thing today: 'What's the number?'I know there will be people here in the Tribulation, but what's the number You're looking for?

00:10:49.040 --> 00:10:58.159
What's the tipping point? What are we waiting on? You say You're waiting on us to bring in the harvest. What's the number? Because I'm a numbers person.

00:10:58.160 --> 00:11:13.679
I'm always thinking, 'Show me what You're looking at so we can at least...'You know when you have those fundraisers and you see the thermometer and they fill in the red as it goes up?

00:11:13.680 --> 00:11:22.478
I'm thinking, at least give me a goal: 14 million, 15 million, 16—no, that's not enough.

00:11:22.479 --> 00:11:28.419
A billion, two billion, three billion. What's on Your heart? He doesn't want any man to perish.

00:11:28.420 --> 00:11:37.492
Well, we've got a problem—I'm just teasing—because I'm thinking there are 8 billion people and I know there's going to be a lot of them in the Tribulation.

00:11:37.493 --> 00:11:46.799
But I'm stretching out and believing God for big. I want to reach the nations for Jesus.

00:11:46.800 --> 00:11:53.119
That's why I'm inspired by people who are already doing it and touching people's lives.

00:11:53.120 --> 00:12:00.078
It's exciting whenever I get your emails and you say, 'Braden, you prayed for this and I was delivered.

00:12:00.079 --> 00:12:07.059
I have no more pains in my body and Jesus set me free through your broadcast.

00:12:07.060 --> 00:12:20.239
I had demonic oppression and depression, and ever since you prayed, I haven't had it anymore.'Just hearing the testimonies—Diana said, 'You hear a lot of the negative, Braden, but I want to go through all the positive ones today.

00:12:20.240 --> 00:12:27.039
I want to show you the ones that are being impacted by the ministry versus the knuckleheads that want to be mean.

00:12:27.040 --> 00:12:40.879
I want to show you the ones whose lives are being forever changed, and it's changing their whole family because of the ministry, Brandon.'So she read through some of those and it blessed me because I don't have time to read all that.

00:12:40.880 --> 00:12:57.519
She reads a lot of it and I just say, 'God bless it.'I'm excited to be here and thankful to hear the testimonies of what the Lord has done on this little YouTube channel.

00:12:57.520 --> 00:13:09.385
We started out three years ago and here we are now. The Lord said, 'I want you to go on mornings now, and then I'll grow it to 20,000 every single day.'20,000 on a live stream.

00:13:09.386 --> 00:13:18.558
I want to grow it to 20,000. So that's my number. I'm believing for 20,000 people to come on in on a live stream and pray with me every single time at once.

00:13:18.559 --> 00:13:26.879
The Lord said, "I'll give you the largest prayer army in the world. A million people will pray with you on a consecutive basis.

00:13:26.880 --> 00:13:42.252
Believe me for it."So I'm believing for a million-man and -woman prayer army to pray over the nations, that when we pray over presidents and politicians around the world, we can change things through the power of prayer.

00:13:42.253 --> 00:13:49.599
I truly believe that the authority of the believer is not being taught in this generation enough.

00:13:49.600 --> 00:14:02.078
We have people like Sister Billie who will go over it and have her book, and Brother Hagin, but he went home and Billy's getting older, so we need another generation, a younger generation, grabbing a hold of it.

00:14:02.079 --> 00:14:09.919
You have authority over the devil, and you can tread on serpents and scorpions, and nothing shall by any means hurt you.

00:14:09.920 --> 00:14:17.299
I believe that we have a covenant-keeping God, that whatsoever things we bind on earth are bound in heaven, and whatsoever things are loosed on earth are loosed in heaven.

00:14:17.300 --> 00:14:22.102
I believe that we have power and authority to tread on those serpents and scorpions.

00:14:22.103 --> 00:14:26.515
And the roaring lion that he thinks he is, we have authority over him.

00:14:26.516 --> 00:14:33.198
He's a toothless lion; he may have a roar, but a lion without teeth is not a threat.

00:14:33.199 --> 00:14:42.559
He cannot devour those that are underneath the covenant. A curse without a cause cannot stand.

00:14:42.560 --> 00:14:46.958
Don't give it a cause. Don't open the doors for the devil to come.

00:14:46.959 --> 00:14:51.669
If you open the door for the devil, he'll come right in on top of you.

00:14:51.670 --> 00:14:54.889
Keep the door shut. How do you do that? By fellowship with him.

00:14:54.890 --> 00:15:03.998
Read your Bible and pray. Take communion every day. When you get real with God, God will become real to you.

00:15:03.999 --> 00:15:09.219
Stop being fake. He knows what you're thinking before you even think it.

00:15:09.220 --> 00:15:14.159
He knows what you're going to say out of your heart. Out of the abundance of the heart, the mouth speaks.

00:15:14.160 --> 00:15:18.638
He knows what you're going to say out of your mouth before you even say it.

00:15:18.639 --> 00:15:26.212
You think, say, whatever; it's about relationship. He knows when I'm mad at him.

00:15:26.213 --> 00:15:35.278
He knows when I'm having a bad day. He knows when I'm upset about what we're going through. So get real with him.

00:15:35.279 --> 00:15:42.958
When you get real with God—and I'm not trying to tell you to be disrespectful; don't ever dishonor him—just be real with him in your heart: "I'm going through this.

00:15:42.959 --> 00:15:53.078
I need you."The more you say, "I need you,"the more you realize that you can't do this without him.

00:15:53.079 --> 00:16:00.575
Humble yourself underneath his mighty hand. I say, "God, help me. I can't do this without you. I need you.

00:16:00.576 --> 00:16:05.838
I need you in every area of my life: spiritually, physically, financially, mentally, emotionally.

00:16:05.839 --> 00:17:41.839
I need you."The first thing this morning, he said, "Happy birthday, Brennan."The moment I woke up, I could tell he was watching me, like he was watching me sleep, anticipating me waking up.

00:17:41.840 --> 00:17:55.553
I saw things yesterday in prayer that make you realize how close we are to the coming of the Lord.

00:17:55.554 --> 00:18:02.393
I'll go into more detail today because I try not to hurry it, but I give you the details.

00:18:02.394 --> 00:18:15.962
As that angel came in yesterday and stood right here, I was praying and singing that song, "Holy, Holy, Holy."The Lord corrected me.

00:18:15.963 --> 00:18:23.599
He said, "You're letting your mind wander too much."When I was praying, he said, "Stop worrying about the time clock. Let it die.

00:18:23.600 --> 00:18:33.678
If they want to leave, they'll leave, but I need you to do something for me today."And that's the same thing he said today about this because I said, "Well, it's my birthday.

00:18:33.679 --> 00:18:48.558
Do I do a video day?"He said, "I need you today to do this."I said, "Okay, we'll do it."So, as the angel was there yesterday, he said, "I have a message for you.

00:18:48.559 --> 00:18:52.819
I want you to say I have a message. The Lord wants you to say this."I saw him.

00:18:52.820 --> 00:18:57.439
He was standing right there, and he had that golden armor on with that helmet on.

00:18:57.440 --> 00:19:04.639
It had a weird-looking hat, a little hair-looking stuff coming off the top of his head that looked like some kind of feathers.

00:19:04.640 --> 00:19:13.999
I've never seen an angel look like that before. It's really neat looking, but I was seeing it in the spirit.

00:19:14.000 --> 00:19:23.620
It wasn't in the natural; I wasn't touching it. I'm looking over in the spirit.

00:19:23.621 --> 00:19:29.999
As I was singing, I saw the wall, the watchman wall, again. This is the second day in a row the Lord allowed me to see that wall.

00:19:30.000 --> 00:19:38.215
And he said, "This is your wall. Which door, which portal do you want to go down today in prayer?"And he let me choose again.

00:19:38.216 --> 00:19:58.159
But I was sitting there singing, and then the angel came and he said to me, "The Lord says, sing the song one more time."I started singing it, but because I was crying, my voice was cracking, and I couldn't hit the higher notes.

00:19:58.160 --> 00:20:04.778
After I sang it halfway through, I looked to see if he was going to say something, and he didn't say anything.

00:20:04.779 --> 00:20:14.079
Then he said, "Sing the song all the way through."I was just taken aback by it. I was like, "Okay."So I sang it again.

00:20:14.080 --> 00:20:26.079
When I got to the end of it, the door that he was standing in front of opened, and I could see the Father on the throne, a big bright light.

00:20:26.080 --> 00:20:32.936
There was a staircase that went down with beautiful water that started to flow from his throne.

00:20:32.937 --> 00:20:41.839
This water that looked just like living water just started flowing down. It was the floodgates of the revival.

00:20:41.840 --> 00:20:48.239
It was the flood of the major outpouring that's about to happen on this earth. It was there; I could see it.

00:20:48.240 --> 00:21:13.447
Then he said, "I have a message."The angel said, "I have a message about Israel."He said, "The fig tree is ripe, and Ezekiel 38-39 is at the door."The fig tree is ripe.

00:21:13.448 --> 00:21:21.659
I saw these vast figs on this fig tree that were double the size of a normal fig, but they looked beautiful.

00:21:21.660 --> 00:21:29.483
It looked like you could just eat the whole tree. This tree was massive, and it was upon a hill.

00:21:29.484 --> 00:21:39.678
I could see the sun setting on the hill. The sun was setting on this dispensation of grace.

00:21:39.679 --> 00:21:48.017
Jesus Christ is coming, ladies and gentlemen, and it's time to get your heart right before him. I saw the fig tree.

00:21:48.018 --> 00:22:07.519
As I was looking into that fig tree, the Lord said, "I have scattered my people upon the earth, and now is the time I will gather them all."He was talking about the Jews.

00:22:07.520 --> 00:22:17.910
He said, "I have scattered them all over the earth, and now I'm going to gather them all."I saw persecution coming on the Jewish people.

00:22:17.911 --> 00:22:29.759
I saw a mass amount of people coming to Israel and Jerusalem and all the area in the days ahead.

00:22:29.760 --> 00:22:43.279
It is a major turning of an event. He said as of this month—the seventh month—it is a significant month: the month of July.

00:22:43.280 --> 00:23:09.279
He said this is a significant month of an acceleration for this next six months: July, August, September, October, November, and December.

00:23:09.280 --> 00:23:34.199
Six months, yes. Over this time frame, I saw an acceleration of things: of elders going home, of a cleansing of the church.

00:23:34.200 --> 00:23:45.999
From July 3rd to January 3rd—the first part of next year—is this time frame of an acceleration of things.

00:23:46.000 --> 00:23:58.158
Thanks, son; I really appreciate that. As I was looking into Israel, I saw a light over it with dark in a valley, and I saw the bones living.

00:23:58.159 --> 00:24:11.439
He said, "Can these bones live concerning America? Can these bones live concerning the revival?"I was praying over the dry bones over the world.

00:24:11.440 --> 00:24:20.439
Talking about the lukewarm, talking about the cold Christians, the people who know better: it's time to come home.

00:24:20.440 --> 00:24:33.119
It's time to become on fire for Jesus. He's coming back for a bride without spot or wrinkle that is holy and brought to his side, not a harlot.

00:24:33.120 --> 00:24:38.959
You're not in bed with two different things. It's all him and none of us, right?

00:24:38.960 --> 00:24:45.821
We need to be sold out to him, and we don't have a compromise of the world inside of us.

00:24:45.822 --> 00:24:55.903
It's time to come up higher in our prayer life. It's time to come up higher in our relationship with the Lord. We need to be all-in.

00:24:55.904 --> 00:25:02.788
As I saw the fig tree upon the hill, I saw the water coming down, and I saw the revival, and I saw creative miracles.

00:25:02.789 --> 00:25:10.479
And they said, 'Do not become familiar with the miracles that you're about to see.

00:25:10.480 --> 00:25:12.239
Don't take them as just another miracle.'Honor them; every miracle is to be holy.

00:25:12.240 --> 00:25:25.119
Don't say, 'It's just another set of blind eyes; it's just another dead man being raised.

00:25:25.120 --> 00:25:35.439
I've seen that before.'Every miracle is a gift from God. It's a blessing. It's his grace.

00:25:35.440 --> 00:25:52.604
He said, 'For now, show me your glory and I will pass by with my goodness and my mercy on this generation.'Oral Roberts had his; Jack Coe had his; William Branham, Kenneth Hagin, Kathryn Kuhlman.

00:25:52.605 --> 00:26:16.945
But the Lord said, 'I'm raising up a new generation, a new era of people right now that you're about to see, who are the closers, built for pressure.'He said, 'This is my dream team.'It's like it was in the '90s when we had Michael Jordan, Magic Johnson, and Larry Bird playing basketball for the Olympics.

00:26:16.946 --> 00:26:23.759
He's putting in his dream team. And ladies and gentlemen, there's many of you that would be the dream team.

00:26:23.760 --> 00:26:29.678
He's raising up prophetic voices with accuracy and without being flaky.

00:26:29.679 --> 00:26:37.278
There's too much flakiness, charismatic weirdness, and the Lord's going to strip away this charismatic weirdness.

00:26:37.279 --> 00:26:45.976
It's embarrassing. You have a group of people that don't know how to hear the Holy Ghost. It's weird; there's a lot of weirdness.

00:26:45.977 --> 00:26:54.497
And the Lord said, 'I'm flipping the status quo concerning finances.'The devil's crowd had it too long.

00:26:54.498 --> 00:27:08.788
And if you listen to what he's telling you to do, he said, 'I'll give you more than enough to do what I need you to do, exceedingly abundantly above all that you'd ask or think.'It's time to believe him for bigger.

00:27:08.789 --> 00:27:15.439
Well, 'I'm just believing for my bills to be paid.'You're believing too small.

00:27:15.440 --> 00:27:24.692
It's not just about 'us four and no more.'It's about stretching out and believing God for exceedingly abundantly above all that you'd ask or think.

00:27:24.693 --> 00:27:43.439
Why? Because God is a covenant-keeping God. And if God did it for Abraham, he'll do it for you. If God did it for Solomon, how much more will he do it for you?

00:27:43.440 --> 00:27:54.959
If Solomon was underneath the old covenant and you're underneath the new, how much more will God do it for you if you believe him for it? But it's produced from seedtime and harvest.

00:27:54.960 --> 00:28:11.119
And a lot of people just sit back on their 'Blessed Assurance'and say, 'Well, I'm going to just sow five dollars and we're going to have enough money to do whatever.'It starts out that way, but if you're faithful with little, he'll make you ruler over much.

00:28:11.120 --> 00:28:19.359
What's in your heavenly account? What are you doing to help your pastor out at your local church?

00:28:19.360 --> 00:28:26.558
'Well, I give him a dollar every time,'and you're worth hundreds of thousands.

00:28:26.559 --> 00:28:34.559
You can't even buy a stick of gum for a buck, but you think that pastor is going to be able to help and do things in his church to be able to get this gospel preached?

00:28:34.560 --> 00:28:50.719
You think, 'Well, I gave him five dollars, Brandon. I tipped him; he gave a good sermon today.'What are you going to do with five dollars?

00:28:50.720 --> 00:28:57.465
It's time to believe God for bigger. But then you look at what?

00:28:57.466 --> 00:28:59.612
Thirty, sixty, a hundredfold. What's in your heavenly account?

00:28:59.613 --> 00:29:09.419
Multiply a hundredfold of five dollars. Does that get you into millionaire status? No. Does that get you in the billionaire flow? No.

00:29:09.420 --> 00:29:16.719
It's a start, but you've got to check your thermostat and how much is in that account.

00:29:16.720 --> 00:29:27.918
That's where I multiply and I look and say, 'Okay, do I have by spiritual law the seed in the ground to believe for the building that the Lord has told me to do?

00:29:27.919 --> 00:29:36.838
Do I have it when he said, I want you to create new TV stations and do these things in the days ahead?'There are things that he's put a mandate on, like having a theater in Branson to do these things.

00:29:36.839 --> 00:29:50.548
But the Lord said, 'Don't ever ask for anything; believe me for it.'The charismatic weirdness—like I said, the Lord said, 'I'm changing things.

00:29:50.549 --> 00:29:58.479
I'm going to do things differently with you and the way you're doing your ministry.

00:29:58.480 --> 00:30:07.759
I don't want it to be like this.'These people are losing their voice with the world.

00:30:07.760 --> 00:30:14.467
They're losing their—what was the word he used? relevance.

00:30:14.468 --> 00:30:19.199
Yeah, he said they're losing their relevance. They're not relevant.

00:30:19.200 --> 00:30:30.719
A lot of these people have lost their voice. And he said, 'Don't do what other men are doing. Do something different.

00:30:30.720 --> 00:30:43.278
Don't lose your voice because of the way you present my gospel.'They had their time and I told them to do that in their time, but behold, I'm doing something new.

00:30:43.279 --> 00:30:51.930
And so I just follow him. You can't go back to the way people did it before.

00:30:51.931 --> 00:31:01.278
God's doing something new in this generation. Well, you know, Oral Roberts did it this way, or somebody else.

00:31:01.279 --> 00:31:15.759
I try to always quote dead people because with the ones that are still alive, with the sin that's being uncovered in a lot of ministries, I try not to link up with anybody.

00:31:15.760 --> 00:31:19.839
I'm just going to stay in my lane because I know what he told me.

00:31:19.840 --> 00:31:23.678
There's a cleaning, and there's a lot of corruption in a lot of ministries.

00:31:23.679 --> 00:31:28.398
And the Lord said, 'I'm dealing with this.'It's embarrassing.

00:31:28.399 --> 00:31:33.039
You represent the King; you've got to get your stuff together.

00:31:33.040 --> 00:31:40.479
And the Lord said to me, 'Stay the course of what I told you to do.'And that's why I've never taken any invitations.

00:31:40.480 --> 00:31:44.398
How many people invite me to come preach at big conferences all the time?

00:31:44.399 --> 00:31:51.999
How many people invite me to come on their TV programs? A lot. I don't do any of it until he says so.

00:31:52.000 --> 00:32:00.158
I stay where he said: 'Go behind your camera.'I want to go here, I want to go there? Nope. 'I called you to be alone right now.

00:32:00.159 --> 00:32:11.119
Go sit on the back row of the church over there and I want you to be there and pray for them.'So I just do what he says and I beat to the drum of what he tells me to do.

00:32:11.120 --> 00:32:20.239
No matter what kind of money's thrown at me, whatever has been offered to me, I go, 'God, I am dead to it.'I know what God has told me.

00:32:20.240 --> 00:32:29.119
There's a select few that will walk in the greater glory, and I'm telling you, I am determined to be one of them.

00:32:29.120 --> 00:32:50.079
I want to be a part of that Holy Ghost and fire that's about to happen, but I don't want my flesh to be so out of control that he says, 'Brandon, I can't use that.'I want to be dead—not dead physically, but dead to whatever my—that's why I try to tell you: find your box.

00:32:50.080 --> 00:33:11.999
If William Seymour was not allowed to go and do his service until he put the box on his head for how long—sometimes they said 45 minutes, sometimes a couple hours—he would sit on the platform at Azusa Street with a wooden crate on his head before the glory would show up.

00:33:12.000 --> 00:33:31.999
